wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sabrina-barry@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sabrina-barry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sabrina-barry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)</a>厚颜无耻地向搭档<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-keoghan">巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan)</a>致意，结束了 2024 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉 (Coachella) 音乐节</a>的最后一场演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/saltburn-review-party-with-the-poshos-in-the-naughty-noughties-3543230">《Saltburn》评论：与顽皮的 20 年代的贵族们一起聚会</a></strong></li></ul><p>4 月 19 日，卡彭特在科切拉音乐节第二个周末在科切拉舞台上表演时，在最后一首诗中向基奥根致敬，基奥根去年主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/saltburn"><em>《索尔特伯恩》</em></a> 。自今年早些时候以来，两人就一直保持着浪漫的联系。</p><p>在《Nonsense》中，萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 在结尾处即兴表演了厚颜无耻的歌词，她唱道： <em>“他的膝盖如此无力，他不得不撑开我的/他像喝红酒一样喝我的洗澡水/科切拉，当我回来时见标题”</em> 。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 在她最后的“废话”结尾中引用了她男友巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 在<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Saltburn?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Saltburn</a>中的浴缸场景：</p><p> “他的膝盖太虚弱了，他不得不撑开我的膝盖。他喝我的洗澡水就像喝红酒一样。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Coachella?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Coachella</a> ，当我成为头条新闻时，再见。” <a href="https://t.co/k7RwPD9bd8">pic.twitter.com/k7RwPD9bd8</a></p><p> - 马库斯 (@marcusuntrell) <a href="https://twitter.com/marcusuntrell/status/1781504394556584237?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 4 月 20 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “洗澡水”歌词引用了<em>《索尔特本》</em>中的一个场景，奥利弗（基奥根饰）在偷看菲利克斯（雅各布·埃洛迪饰）在浴缸里自慰后喝了他的洗澡水。</p><p>在科切拉音乐节表演结束后，卡彭特回顾了她在音乐节上的两场演出，写道：“那是我参加过的最有趣的演出之一。我不敢相信我能和唯一一位伟大的[​​诺拉琼斯]一起唱“不知道为什么”......。我不敢相信我的键盘被闹鬼了……我不敢相信你们已经在跟着唱“浓缩咖啡”中的所有歌词了。我觉得自己很幸运。谢谢各位前来观看！！！！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5_tD2fyB5H/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.