>Oasis</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">Mariah Carey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-o-connor">Sinead O&#39;Connor</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sade">Sade</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiction">Jane&#39;s Addiction</a> 、Eric B. &amp; Rakim 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lenny-kravitz">Lenny Kravitz</a> 。</p><p>去年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-bush">凯特·布什</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-michael">乔治·迈克尔</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-bush-and-george-michael-are-among-2023-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-inductees-3438846">入选摇滚名人堂仪式的艺术家之一。</a> 2023 年的其他入选者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">Sheryl Crow</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a>的乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">Rage Against The Machine</a> 、说唱创新者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-eliott">Missy Eliott</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-spinners">The Spinners</a>和乡村传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/willie-nelson">Willie Nelson。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">2024 年摇滚名人堂后：奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)、雪儿 (Cher) 等将入选的人物</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
